title: Sheep and livestock causing A595 delays | Border
text:
Sheep and livestock are on the road. Credit: Franz-Peter Tschauner/DPA/Press Association Images The A595 has been partially blocked after an accident involving a trailer carrying sheep and livestock.
Sheep are on the road, causing delays both ways between A689 / Peter Lane and Wigton Road / Queensway.
Police are directing traffic.
Last updated Thu 17 Sep 2015 Travel Cumbria A595
